<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> cuntara<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu patineṭṭāvatu malāṭāṉa <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ṉanātavaḷa nāṭṭuk kuṟukkaik kūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yañ ciṟṟiṅkūr <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom tiruppulippakavarkku tiruviḻā Eḻuntaruḷumpotu muṉ niṉṟu nirttañ ceyya nirttappo
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kamāka tiruppulippakavar nirttaviṭaṅkikkum Ivaḷaṉṉuvayattukkum ceytu kuṭutta nilamāvatu Eṅkaḷūrt teṉ
<lb n="4"/>piṭākai ko<unclear>li</unclear>yūril kiḻkaḻaniyiṟ peruvāykkālukku vaṭakku tāṉattār nilattukku meṟku kālcey Iṟai
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yiliyāka <hi rend="grantha">candrāditya</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">t</hi> ceykuṭuttom <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yo<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmāheśvara rakṣai <g type="danda">.</g><g type="danda">.</g><g type="danda">.</g>§</hi>
</p>

